<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1940-10-29T10:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1940-10-29T10:00:00-05:00" n="439" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d439">
                                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.0011 European War 1939/6327:
                                    Telegram</note>
                                <head>
                                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in France</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Matthews</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                            State</gloss>
                                    </hi>
                                </head>
                                <opener>
                                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                                        <placeName>
                                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Vichy</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-10-29T17:00:00+02:00">October 29, 1940—5 p.m.</date>
                                        <lb/> [Received 9:20 p.m.]</dateline>
                                </opener>
                                <p>852. I called this afternoon on the Greek Minister to express
                                    indignation at the act of aggression to which his country has
                                    been subjected.</p>
                                <p>He had no news of the day’s developments nor of the attitude
                                    which either Turkey or Bulgaria may assume. The Foreign Office
                                    likewise has no news.</p>
                                <closer>
                                    <signed>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Matthews</hi>
                                    </signed>
                                </closer>
                            </div>
                            </body></text></TEI>